room_title: Escape room "Beyond Medusa's Gate VR" by The Rabbit Hole VR in Nashville
review: Just did a combo package to play Episode 1 and 2 at The Rabbit Hole VR. WHAT A BLAST!!! The staff are so helpful and friendly at The Rabbit Hole VR. I can't wait to try out more rooms. WE WILL BE BACK!
